title: Disney's Winnie The Pooh Preschool
description:
For Ages 2 to 4

Preschoolers gain an understanding of letter and number recognition phonics sequencing and more through a magical Winnie the Pooh story-based journey in the 100 Acre Wood. As preschoolers help Pooh throw a birthday party and attend Christopher Robin&#039;s friendship celebration, they obtain lessons on the importance of friendship and helping others. Builds 20 key skills and includes learning themes inspired by Winnie the Pooh. Adjustable levels to enhance childrens individual skill levels. Progress report provides feedback on skill progression. Printable Winnie the Pooh workbook reinforces skills gained from the learning activities. Encouraging interaction with Pooh and his friends helps build self confidence.

	
	Features & Specifications
	
System requirements

PC Requirements-Windows 95 or later . 90MHz Pentium Processor . 30MB Hard Drive space . 16MB RAM . 4X CD-ROM . 256 color monitor . 16 bit DirectX-compatible sound card . color printer optional

MAC Requirements-7.6.1 system or later . Power PC 75MHz or faster . 25MB Hard Drive space . 24MB-RAM . 4X CD-ROM . 256 color monitor . color printer optional.
